  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: d01fd2d64a9249049aaa77d5c12a82fe, type: 3}
  m_Name: Page 15
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  questionText: Can you think of a reason for the application of petroleum jelly?
  referenceImage: {fileID: 0}
  explanationText: We need an airtight setup to prevent the entry of carbon dioxide
    into the tube. Petroleum jelly is used to fulfill the purpose.
  options:
  - To allow smooth opening of the cork.
  - 'To make the setup airtight by preventing the entry of CO2. '
  - Both A and B
  - None of the above
  correctOptionIndex: 1
